*   ## **_RODERICK STRONG AND TRENT DEF. ORANGE CASSIDY AND WILL OSPREAY_**
    

Great match with a crowd that seemed significantly more energized than recent weeks. Wardlow takes out Will Ospreay allowing Roddy and Trent to take the win.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/9bc240a9-eafb-41c4-982e-48ec5d2dbb64/20240522_172038.jpg?format=original)

Post match, Orange Cassidy and Will Ospreay get beaten down in the ring by Trent and Undesputed Kingdom. Don Callis only shows concern for Orange Cassidy tho.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/a1c10d09-d582-41f9-9e7f-b8d837671d4d/20240522_172837.jpg?format=original)

The Young Bucks have barred Darby Allin from the building

