“WHAT UP, TURDS?”

Swerve to the EVPS

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/f049885e-d962-4535-bb52-a413ab8b3220/20240522_182853.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_SWERVE DEF. NICK WAYNE_**
    

Swerve runs through Nick Wayne in a match that really should’ve taken place in Washington last week.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/fe86fdfb-8a1c-4f3c-b5ce-bddfca14ce21/Screenshot_20240522_182510.jpg?format=original)

Christian Cage attacks Swerve but runs away and tries to drive away from the arena after Swerve takes out Luchasaurus/Killswitch.

But Christian won’t get away this time. Prince Nana returns to cut off Christian and his stolen truck. Swerve yanks him out of the window. Brawls with Christian on the roof of the car and DDTs him.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/8ad9ff8e-7690-44a9-9e25-6111f3f0990c/20240522_182850.jpg?format=original)

