*   ## **_Bryan Danielson def. Satnum Singh by DQ_**
    

Planet Jarrett try to collect the bounty on Bryan's head by taking him out. They're paid off and the Elite begin to take out Bryan.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/7ef44902-e30c-46bd-bc43-e34eda1ac971/20240522_190616.jpg?format=original)

TONY KHAN IS BACK AND HE'S PROVIDED DARBY ALLIN WITH A RIDE TO DYNAMITE AND A FREAKING FLAMETHROWER!!!!!!!!!

A video plays on screen, Tony Khan drives up to the building. Darby Allin comes out of the back seat with a flamethrower.

Darby runs out, outs Nick Jackson through a table and clears the way for Bryan and Darby to stand tall for Team AEW